Paper: hep-th/9711120

Date: 1997-11-18

Title: A Superspace Normal Coordinate Derivation of the Density Formula

Authors: Marcus T. Grisaru, Marcia E. Knutt-Wehlau, Warren Siegel

Comments: 16 pages, latex

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B523 (1998) 663-679

Using normal coordinate expansions we derive by purely superspace methods thedensity formula giving the component action corresponding to a superspacesupergravity-matter action.